Threshold - March Of Progress  mp3  320k  a2k  2012  What we got...March of Progress is the ninth studio album (and sixteenth overall) by progressive metal band Threshold. It is the first studio album on which original lead vocalist Damian Wilson sings since his return in 2009. It is also their second album on their current label, Nuclear Blast. The Limited Edition includes a bonus track, "Divinity."
